intro:"Python reads almost like plain English. Every programmer starts with the same first step — printing text to the screen.",
concepts:[{i:"🐍",t:"Python",d:"A readable high-level language used in AI, data science, and web development."},{i:"📣",t:"print()",d:"The most fundamental command — displays text or values on screen."},{i:"💬",t:"String",d:"Text always wrapped in quotes: 'hello' or \"hello\"."},{i:"#",t:"Comment",d:"A line starting with # that Python ignores. Use it for notes."}],
